summary: In this blog post, I explore the concept of an "agent harness" — the combination of tools, environment, hard controls, and soft controls that shapes what an AI agent can and cannot do. I illustrate these ideas with three real-world examples. Curious how these controls impact the behavior and capabilities of different agents? Read on to find out!
